SUMMARY:Swann Park Improvements Community Meeting
LOCATION:Kate Jackson Community Center 821 South Rome Avenue Tampa \, FL 3
 3606 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Tampa Parks and Recreation Department for the
  first community meeting for the Swann Park Improvements Project. Park pat
 rons are invited to learn about proposed park enhancements\, review prelim
 inary concepts and share feedback. Community input will help inform future
  project decisions and contribute to creating a welcoming\, family-friendl
 y park that reflects the needs and priorities of the community. The meetin
 g will take place on Tuesday\, July 7\, from 6 p.m. to 7 p.m. at the Kate 
 Jackson Community Center\, 821 South Rome Avenue. Participation is availab
 le both in person and virtually. Visit tampa.govSwanPark to learn more and
  register for virtual participation. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/
 node/191801
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191801
END:VEVENT
