 t
LOCATION:2223 N Westshore Blvd Ste 140 Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:World renown visual artist Romero BRITTO is coming to Tampa! J
 oin us for the Grand Opening Event on Saturday\, July 11th! 1pm Ribbon Cut
 ting\, Drinks\, Live DJ\, Artist Appearance\, and Signing Session in Store
 ! Join us for the grand opening event of BRITTO at International Plaza Bay
  Street in Tampa\, FL! Get ready for a day filled with art\, fun\, and cel
 ebration on July\, 11th at 1:00 PM (Eastern Time). Experience the vibrant 
