SUMMARY:Freedom\, Food Fitness Festival
LOCATION:1345 W. Main Street Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for an unforgettable day of energy\, empowerment\, a
 nd community at the Freedom\, Food and Fitness Fest ! Join us for a dynami
 c\, family-friendly experience where culture\, wellness\, and connection c
 ome together in one vibrant space. From the moment you arrive\, youll be i
 mmersed in a lively atmosphere filled with live performances \, high-energ
 y fitness demos \, and thought-provoking panel discussions designed to ins
 pire and inform. Come hungry and explore a variety of delicious food truck
 s \, connect with community resources including voter registration \, and 
 enjoy activities for all ages. Whether youre looking to move your body\, e
 xpand your knowledge\, or simply enjoy a great day with the communitythis 
 is an event you dont want to miss. Vendor spots are limited\, so dont wait
 secure your place today and be part of a celebration thats all about freed
 om\, health\, and community. Click Here for Vendor Registration (https:das
