SUMMARY:Teen Stay Play Culinary Class
LOCATION:Springhill Park Community Center 1000 E Eskimo Ave. Tampa \, FL 3
 3604 United States
DESCRIPTION:The City of Tampa invites youth to experience the excitement o
 f cooking\, learning\, and leading through our fantastic culinary program\
 , offered at Stay Play locations across the city! Our hands-on program tea
 ches more than recipes  campers build leadership\, sharpen public speaking
  skills\, practice teamwork\, and explore the arts and science of fine foo
 ds. Working together in small groups\, youth learn how to plan\, prepare\,
  and present delicious dishes while striving for one shared goal: creating
  a plate of perfection. We cover kitchen safety\, healthy food choices\, a
 nd sanitary and safety measures for food and utensils. Every session is de
 signed to inspire confidence\, responsibility\, and fun\, all while encour
 aging young chefs to discover new talents and flavors. \n\nPermalink: http
 s://www.tampa.gov/node/191351
