 a FL 33612 Each meeting features expert speakers sharing the latest inform
 ation about lung cancer\, along with time to connect with others who under
 stand the journey. This Months Topic: Adaptive Radiotherapy: Personalizing
  Radiation Treatment for Lung Cancer Guest Speaker: Stephen Rosenberg A fr
 ee lunch is provided\, so please register at least 24 hours in advance. Re
