 ing realistic everyday actions that support better blood sugar control and
  overall health. Participants will leave with practical\, easy-to-apply st
 rategies to build healthier habits and take proactive steps toward prevent
 ion and wellness. August 13\, 2026 Martie Hale RDN 12- 12:45 pm Register H
